Verse 1
Let me start by saying this,
is something that u already have heard
But u gotta find the heart in my words.
There's a deeper meaning that you missed,
do u remember how it felt when we kissed?

I don't take your love lightly
Girl I went all in, I gave all of me.
But I still fucked up, Yea I know I screwed up. 
Just want u to understand that all.

Hook
I wanna do
I wish there was a way, to make it all ok
Is hit undo
Trust me baby, no other man's gonna love you more.
I wanna do
If only I could do it girl just know I would  
is hit undo.

Verse 2
See what went down was too crazy
Never thought she'd ever come at me that way
['cause I kept it real with how I feel]
about you 
So she knew that I was committed, and wasn't tryna get it.
[But still] 
She kept on pursuing me 
[and still] 
She the one who kissed me
This aint an excuse, because she hit home run
But I promise you, I wish it was undone. 

Bridge
Everything that I have 
Girl I'd give it up for you.
If you gave me a shot baby know that i'd come through.
There aint no other way to stop me from goin insane.
The only remedy is hearing you calling my name saying
I forgive u, ill take u back, lets put it behind us, and move from where we were at.
Life without you's like harmonies with a melody thats missin
